title: Bend Sinister - Through the Broken City
description:
These guys are actually from Vancouver, but they played used to play Kelowna a bunch. Close enough I figure. One of the best bands to hit the scene. Check out some of their more recent albums, and go see them if they come near your town. Great band.

Kelowna is a small town in British Columbia, Canada. We have a great local music scene, and with a bit of stimulus, it could be even better. Please seed, please tell your friends about what this town has to offer. Hit up www.kelownagigs.com and come out to a show. I guarantee you'll have a good time, and you'll here some great tunes.
